Name: COVER OR PROTECTION LEVEL
Explanation: SPECIFIES THE LEVEL OF PROTECTION OR COVER. REF AENGRP-2.

Name: DEFENDED ASSET LEVEL OF PROTECTION
Explanation: THE LEVEL OF PROTECTION TO BE PROVIDED TO A DEFENDED ASSET AS AGREED BY THE JDAWG, RATING FROM LEVEL ONE TO LEVEL FOUR.

Name: DEGREE OF PROTECTION, ENVIRONMENTAL
Explanation: THE DEGREE OF PROTECTION PROVIDED FOR PERSONNEL AND/OR WEAPONS-ASSOCIATED FACILITIES, AGAINST ATTACKS BY AIRCRAFT, ARTILLERY, OR MISSILES, IN TERMS OF THEIR IMMEDIATE ENVIRONMENT.
